item.description:
The Kounadis family has been welcoming guests to the Yarmouth House Restaurant for well over two decades. Your hosts take pride in presenting their guests the ultimate in excellent dining and have made the Yarmouth House one of Cape Cod’s most popular dining experiences.

 

You can check out the menu at www.yarmouthhouse.com!  Gale is working on coupons for everyone so you can save some moola!
item.how_to_find_us: Ask for the Girls Just Wanna Have Fun Table!
